data.description: SELLER OFFERING A $5000 BUYER INCENTIVE TO USE A BUYER WANTS! THIS OPEN FLOOR PLAN HOME IS LIKE NEW, BUILT IN 2020. NO PETS OR CHILDREN HAVE LIVED IN THE HOME. THIS BEAUTIFUL HOME HAS IT ALL!! GRANITE COUNTER TOPS, LARGE PRIMARY SUITE ON THE MAIN LEVEL WITH OVER SIZED SHOWER, DOUBLE VANITY'S AND A NICE SOAKING TUB. THERE IS A FORMAL DINING ROOM, A SITTING ROOM, LAUNDRY ROOM HAS OVER SIZED SINK WITH GRANIT COUNTER TOP, TWO BEDROOMS UPSTAIRS AND A BOUNUS ROOM WITH A SINK, TWO LARGE STORAGE AREAS ONE COULD BE MADE INTO ANOTHER ROOM, (ALREADY FRAMED FOR IT), FULLY SCREENED IN PORCH, FRONT YARD IRRIGATION, INDOOR AND OUTDOOR SECURITY SYSTEM, AND A SURROUND SOUND SYSTEM INSIDE AND OUTSIDE OF THE HOME. THE HOME IS 31 MILES FROM FAYETTEVILLE AND 30 MILES FROM RALEIGH, DON'T WAIT TO SEE THIS HOME, IT WON'T BE ON THE MARKET LONG! VA ASSUMABLE AT 2.65%  BE SURE TO TAKE THE VIRTUAL TOUR!!
